{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1683-01_161", "resp": "nbb"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur un Torrent. Sonnet"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", janvier 1683 [tome 1], p. 161-164"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Madame des Marais, Fille de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " Berrier, Secretaire du Conseil, & Femme de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[3]", "text": " Huraut, Comte des Marais, est aussi morte depuis peu de jours. Elle n’avoit que 32. ans. De pareilles morts nous font tous les jours connoistre, que nous n’avons point de jours assurez, & qu’il n’y a rien qui passe si viste. C’est une pensée que vous trouverez exprimée d’une maniere fort spirituelle dans le Sonnet que vous allez voir. Il est fait sur le sujet d’un Torrent, qui a esté proposé dans quelqu’une de mes Lettres."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "SUR UN TORRENT."}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sonnet"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Miroir vaste & pompeux des plus belles journées,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu me fais concevoir par ce rapide cours,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Que comme tu te perds apres ces grands détours,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Un cours presque insensible emporte mes années."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "A peine les reçois-je, elles sont terminées."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "L’instant de leur croissant m’en marque le décours ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Enfin, comme tes eaux, elles sont tous les jours"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Rapides, sans retour, orageuses, bornées."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais tu m’instruis de plus par ta rapidité,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Que je cours dans le sein de la Divinité,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[3]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Si j’ay le cœur exempt d’attache criminelle ;"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[3]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[3]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Que suivant les moyens qui doivent m’y mener,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Je dispose mon cours à la Source eternelle,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[4]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Puis qu’en estant sorty, je dois y retourner."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}]}